  "issue_title": "`AsyncioSelectorReactorTests` are still failing with Python 3.14: \"There is no current event loop in thread 'MainThread'.\"",
  "issue_body": "**Describe the incorrect behavior you saw**\nSome of the \"There is no current event loop in thread 'MainThread'.\" instances seem to have been fixed already, but i'm seeing one more in `test_asyncioreactor`. FWICS this test are skipped on the CI for some reason, so I've figured out I'll report it in case it's missed:\n\n```pytb\n===============================================================================\n[ERROR]\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/tmp/twisted/src/twisted/internet/test/test_asyncioreactor.py\", line 125, in test_newSelectorEventLoopFromDefaultEventLoopPolicy\n    event_loop = self.newLoop(DefaultEventLoopPolicy())\n  File \"/tmp/twisted/src/twisted/internet/test/test_asyncioreactor.py\", line 77, in newLoop\n    existingLoop = get_event_loop()\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3.14/asyncio/events.py\", line 715, in get_event_loop\n    raise RuntimeError('There is no current event loop in thread %r.'\nbuiltins.RuntimeError: There is no current event loop in thread 'MainThread'.\n\ntwisted.internet.test.test_asyncioreactor.AsyncioSelectorReactorTests.test_newSelectorEventLoopFromDefaultEventLoopPolicy\n```\n\n**Describe how to cause this behavior**\n\n```\nuv venv -p 3.14\nuv pip install -e . hypothesis pytest pyhamcrest httpx\n.venv/bin/trial -j12 twisted\n```\n\n**Describe the correct behavior you'd like to see**\nTests passing :-).\n\n**Testing environment**\n - Operating System and Version; paste the output of these commands:\n```console\n$ uname -a\nLinux pomiot 7.0.2-gentoo-dist #1 SMP PREEMPT_DYNAMIC Mon Apr 27 19:01:22 -00 2026 x86_64 AMD Ryzen 5 3600 6-Core Processor AuthenticAMD GNU/Linux\n$ cat /etc/lsb-release\nDISTRIB_ID=\"Gentoo\"\n```\n\n - Twisted version [e.g. 22.2.0]\n```console\n$ twist --version\n25.5.0.post0\n$ uv pip freeze\nanyio==4.13.0\nattrs==26.1.0\nautomat==25.4.16\ncertifi==2026.4.22\nconstantly==23.10.4\nh11==0.16.0\nhttpcore==1.0.9\nhttpx==0.28.1\nhyperlink==21.0.0\nhypothesis==6.152.4\nidna==3.13\nincremental==24.11.0\niniconfig==2.3.0\npackaging==26.2\npluggy==1.6.0\npygments==2.20.0\npyhamcrest==2.1.0\npytest==9.0.3\nsortedcontainers==2.4.0\n-e file:///tmp/twisted\ntyping-extensions==4.15.0\nzope-interface==8.4\n```\n - Reactor [e.g. select, iocp]\n\n\n**Additional context**\nReproduced on 2d196123264efb0027eecfe1b430be4a9babdbd8.\n",
